SUMMARY:Stretch Break
LOCATION:(Hanna Square - Outside) 2555 E Hanna Ave Tampa \, FL United Stat
 es
DESCRIPTION:May is Mental Health Awareness Month and National Physical Fit
 ness Sports Month. Join our stretch breaks this month to support your body
  and mind. Just a few minutes of movement can reduce stress\, improve focu
 s\, and boost energy throughout your day. Keep Moving\, Keep Growing Welln
 ess is built through consistent small actions  Bonus Perks!  No registrati
 on required  just show up!  Prizes for all participants (while supplies la
 st)  Counts toward Optum Engage incentives  Questions? Coach Stef - cotcoa
 chuhc.com 813-535-0482 \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/189671
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/189671
