SUMMARY:Artist Talk: Vaughn Spann in Conversation
LOCATION:120 W Gasparilla Plaza Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an engaging conversation with artist Vaughn Spann.
  Presented in conjunction with the exhibition Vaughn Spann: Allegories at 
 the Tampa Museum of Art\, this program offers an opportunity to hear the a
 rtist discuss his Marked Men series alongside his broader artistic practic
 e and evolving body of work. Spann will be joined in conversation by Joann
 a Robotham\, Curator of Modern and Contemporary Art at the Tampa Museum of
  Art. Lectures are offered free with the cost of daily admission: Art Muse
 um Members: Free Not-Yet-Members: 25 College Students: Free \n\nPermalink:
