SUMMARY:Artist Talk with Zack Wittman\, one of the photographers behind Ci
 gars!
LOCATION:1630 E. 7th Avenue Tampa \, FL 33605 United States
DESCRIPTION:Join us on Thursday\, July 2nd to hear from Zack Wittman\, co-
 creator of Cigar City (2025). Created in collaboration with Americas last 
 operating cigar factory\, J.C. Newman Cigar Company\, the book offers a ph
 otographic exploration of the citys founding industry. Zack will discuss h
 is images of the 24 remaining cigar factories\, each preserved in varying 
 states of decay and adaptation. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/
 190321
